reviewText: Yes not as good as prior DVDs from Banco Popular.

I bought it to enjoy with my family in Christmas Eve, but I was very disappointed. It does't compare with previous productions from Banco Popular. I was expecting more music and less lecturing, more entertainment and less talk. I hope it gets better next year.
It's was not as good as some of the older banco popular DVDs . It's part of my collection so have to take the bad with the good
